  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Ialbum
    The album class allows for the creation of an album instance.
    Ibackend
    The backend class allows for the creation of a backend instance.
    Iphoto
    The photo class allows for the creation of a photo object.
    Itag
    The tag class allows for a creation of a tag object, with methods to return the type of the tag, the value of the tag, as well as methods setType to change the type of tag and setValue to change the value of the tag.
    IUser
    The User class allows for the creation of a User object.
